1. *Bazu* je postavio u dvorište. (He set up a base in the yard.)
2. On je otišao u *bazu*. (He went to the base.)
3. Ona je tražila *bazu*. (She was looking for a base.)
4. On je stvorio novu *bazu*. (He created a new base.)
5. Ona je pronašla *bazu*. (She found the base.)
6. Oni su smislili *bazu*. (They devised a base.)